// NodeContextMenu
// Right-click context menu for nodes in the diagram editor.
// Provides: Edit Label, Change Type (submenu), Add Transition, Delete Node.
// Closes on outside click or Escape.

MenuItem, Divider, TypeSubmenu are layout primitives within the menu.
TypeSubmenu renders a list of type options (terminal/state/decision/action)
with the current type shown in bold.

FUNCTION NodeContextMenu(nodeId, nodeType, position, onEditLabel, onChangeType, onAddTransition, onDelete, onClose) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Renders a positioned menu at the given screen coordinates.
  Closes on mousedown outside the menu element.
  Closes on Escape key.

---

FUNCTION handleEditLabel() -> void
  Prompts user for new label. IF not null, calls onEditLabel(newLabel). Closes.

---

FUNCTION handleTypeSelect(newType) -> void
  Calls onChangeType(newType). Closes.

---

FUNCTION handleAddTransition() -> void
  Calls onAddTransition (enters transition-start selection mode). Closes.

---

FUNCTION handleDelete() -> void
  Confirms with user. IF confirmed, calls onDelete. Closes.
